entries.journal_entry_description: The Civilian Protection guild representative on Kashyyyk wants to speak with you about recent encounters with hostile pirates.
entries.journal_entry_title: Contact Eyma of the Civilian Protection guild
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You will find the venerable Nautolan named 'Eyma' located in a Wookiee hut in the city of Kachirho. Tell him everything you know about recent hostilities in Kashyyyk space.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Talk to Eyma of the Civilian Protection Guild
